                                         JOHANNESBURG - A taxi driver has been killed after being shot multiple times in Umbilo in Durban. Paramedics say they found the man with multiple gunshot wounds when they arrived at the scene this morning.  The motive behind the shooting is not known at this stage. Rescue Care’s Garrith Jamieson said, “A male believed to be in his 20s was found inside his taxi, the police will be investigating further.” 